    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "31580165_4_2326-2377",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2326-2377",
      "markText": "夫以无识之物，郁然有彩20；有心之器，其无文欤！",
      "totalCount": 252,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=31580165&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2326&rangeEnd=2377",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d0732ff071e1e005d073eab?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2326&rangeEnd=2377"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "31580165_5_672-710",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "672-710",
      "markText": "本篇主旨在说明写作文章，必须以圣人的作品及其指导性言论为依据，故名《征圣》。",
      "totalCount": 238,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=31580165&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=672&rangeEnd=710",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d0732ff071e1e005d073eab?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=672&rangeEnd=710"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "31580165_4_770-811",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "770-811",
      "markText": "文表现为形态色泽之美，也表现为音响声韵之美。它们都是自然而然地形成的，是道的体现。",
      "totalCount": 221,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=31580165&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=770&rangeEnd=811",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d0732ff071e1e005d073eab?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=770&rangeEnd=811"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "31580165_4_7075-7091",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "7075-7091",
      "markText": "辞之所以能鼓天下者，乃道之文也。",
      "totalCount": 216,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=31580165&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=7075&rangeEnd=7091",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d0732ff071e1e005d073eab?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=7075&rangeEnd=7091"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "31580165_29_2272-2303",
      "chapterUid": 29,
      "range": "2272-2303",
      "markText": "登山则情满于山，观海则意溢于海，我才之多少，将与风云而并驱矣。",
      "totalCount": 210,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=31580165&chapterUid=29&rangeStart=2272&rangeEnd=2303",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d0732ff071e1e005d073eab?chapterUid=29&rangeStart=2272&rangeEnd=2303"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "31580165_4_709-735",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "709-735",
      "markText": "天色玄，地色黄，天上日月垂光，地上山川焕采，都是文。",
      "totalCount": 198,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=31580165&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=709&rangeEnd=735",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d0732ff071e1e005d073eab?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=709&rangeEnd=735"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "31580165_5_6025-6152",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "6025-6152",
      "markText": "赞曰：妙极生知1，睿哲惟宰2。精理为文，秀气成采。鉴悬日月，辞富山海。百龄影徂3，千载心在。",
      "totalCount": 192,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=31580165&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=6025&rangeEnd=6152",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d0732ff071e1e005d073eab?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=6025&rangeEnd=6152"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "31580165_3_588-644",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "588-644",
      "markText": "《文心雕龙》是中国中古时期一部伟大的理论批评著作，在中国文学批评、文章学、修辞学的发展历史中，都占有重要的地位。",
      "totalCount": 182,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=31580165&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=588&rangeEnd=644",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d0732ff071e1e005d073eab?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=588&rangeEnd=644"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "31580165_29_2413-2428",
      "chapterUid": 29,
      "range": "2413-2428",
      "markText": "意翻空而易奇，言征实而难巧也。",
      "totalCount": 180,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=31580165&chapterUid=29&rangeStart=2413&rangeEnd=2428",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d0732ff071e1e005d073eab?chapterUid=29&rangeStart=2413&rangeEnd=2428"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "31580165_29_8296-8479",
      "chapterUid": 29,
      "range": "8296-8479",
      "markText": "赞曰：神用象通1，情变所孕。物以貌求，心以理应。刻镂声律2，萌芽比兴3。结虑司契4，垂帷制胜5。",
      "totalCount": 170,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=31580165&chapterUid=29&rangeStart=8296&rangeEnd=8479",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d0732ff071e1e005d073eab?chapterUid=29&rangeStart=8296&rangeEnd=8479"
    },
